Title: Squeaky Toy of Time and Space
Description:
We have detected another time anomaly. A strange object that even we cannot understand the significance of.

This artifact must be returned before it does irreparable damage to the true timeline and the world as we know it.

Return here once you have recovered the artifact. I will open a portal so you may return it to its proper place.
ObjectivesText: Find the Time-Displaced Toy and return it to its proper time.
CompletionText: All of our fates depend on returning that artifact to its proper time.
RewardText: Thank you, champion. You have helped save Azeroth once again. I shudder to think what would have happened, were you not here to intervene...

Objectives.Text: Take portal from Everywhen Inn to Naxxramas
Return to Soridormi in Everywhen Inn
Take the portal from Naxxramas to Everywhen Inn
